The paper discusses the development of a search engine using neural networks and BERT embeddings to improve the search results for complex queries. This falls under the category of Information Retrieval (cs.IR) as well as Natural Language Processing (cs.CL). The use of neural networks and embeddings also suggests the involvement of Machine Learning (cs.LG), Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI), and Deep Learning (cs.DL) sub-categories.
